    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136880/extras/7c30e72a0cdf1af3605cbe9029db534b.avif?t=1764928140\" width=601 height=219 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >担任学生会干部与动漫社部长的‘我’，原本能在形形色色的人中左右逢源，但近来却不可避免的卷入到人际交往的冲突中。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在与傲娇直率的学妹江沐橙争吵之后，又哄骗着外冷内热的白筱筱，虽然维系关系的平衡十分艰难，但‘我’还算得心应手。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >直到……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136880/extras/ee6dd1bebe01afe114e60cb6e331a831.avif?t=1764928140\" width=491 height=363 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136880/extras/724bea1082ee16e304f6672d90fa706c.avif?t=1764928140\" width=601 height=632 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136880/extras/009740f60851e597e20b72047c1aaef0.avif?t=1764928140\" width=602 height=632 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《我与她们的大学画相》是一篇轻松愉快的短篇galgame，虽然是短篇，但一样拥有有可供选择的路线分支剧情，多结局故事路线等功能，我们会根据反馈进行不断的优化，期待与你早日相见！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家交流群：<strong>670183360</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果想了解更多讯息！也可以于交流群咨询！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >注：Win11+N卡驱动576以上，满足两点会因为引擎原因而无法启动</p>",
